What is inheritance:

through inheretance mchanism we can get the properties and methods
from the parent class inside the child class.

Why we should use inheritance;

Reduce amount of code.
2)More efficient
3) Saves memory

how we can use:
1)Create a parent class. use the extend keyword
2)Put all the common methods and properties from children classes inside that parent class.
3)use extend keyword to inherit from that parent class




Rules :

1) Private fields and private methods can not be inherited inside the children classes.
2)constructor wont inhereit

Represent IS-A relationship which is parent to child relationship

Types:
Single inheritance--> Single parent class and single child class
Multilevel inheritance
Hierarchical inheritance